### ============================================================================
### AUTENTICAÇÃO
### ============================================================================

### 1. Registrar um novo usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teste@ifrs.edu.br",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "ALUNO"
}

### 2. Fazer login (obter token JWT)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teste@ifrs.edu.br",
  "password": "123456"
}

### ============================================================================
### CARDÁPIOS/MENUS (Todas as rotas exigem autenticação)
### ============================================================================

### 3. Obter cardápios da semana atual
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu/current-week
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Obter cardápios do dia atual
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu/current-day
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Obter cardápio da próxima refeição (baseado na hora atual)
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu/current
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Obter todos os cardápios
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Obter cardápio por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Criar um novo cardápio
POST {{baseUrl}}/menu
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "type": "ALMOCO",
  "date": "2026-05-05",
  "items": ["Arroz", "Feijão", "Carne", "Salada"]
}

### 9. Atualizar um cardápio
PUT {{baseUrl}}/menu/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "type": "JANTAR",
  "date": "2026-05-05",
  "items": ["Macarrão", "Frango", "Legumes"]
}

### 10. Deletar um cardápio
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/menu/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}